CONGRESSMAN Eric "Gang Bang on da Fang Fang" Swalwell has refused to say if he had sex with an alleged Chinese spy ‚Äî claiming the information is "classified".

He was one of a number of Democrats targeted in a honey trap operation to infiltrate political circles, according to bombshell reports last night.

Overseas student Christine Fang ‚Äî known as Fang Fang ‚Äî is said to have been taped by the FBI having sex with two Midwestern mayors.

She also cozied up to a string of other politicians including presidential hopeful Tulsi Gabbard before mysteriously vanishing.

Swalwell, who is now a member of the House Intelligence Committee, is the most high profile figure to be swept up in the alleged scandal.

Last night Fox News anchor Tucker Carlson claimed security agencies believe he was in a sexual relationship with the suspected spy.

And Donald Trump Jr told the show it meant Swalwell was a "threat to national security."

Carlson told viewers: "US intelligence officials believe that Fang had a sexual relationship with Eric Swalwell.

"We asked Swalwell's office about that directly today.

"His staff replied by saying that they could not comment whether Swalwell had a sexual relationship with Fang, because that information might be, quote, classified."

Swalwell, 40, was unmarried at the time he met Fang in around 2012. He would wed Brittany Watts in 2016.

She is said to have raise funds and campaigned for him among Asian American voters as head of a student group.

According to a report by Axios, he cut off contact with Fang after a "defensive briefing" from FBI agents who were investigating her.

Swalwell's office told The Sun: "Rep Swalwell, long ago, provided information about this person ‚Äî whom he met more than eight years ago, and whom he hasn‚Äôt seen in nearly six years ‚Äî to the FBI.

"To protect information that might be classified, he will not participate in your story."

There is a Reason this F##ktard is kicked Off of the Intelligence Committee.

Same goes for Adam Schiff for Brains (D-CA)

Hunter Biden Did Not Register as an Agent of a Foreign Coutry, But He Was in Violation of the Law

Hunter Biden lobbied for Burisma and even tried to wrangle visas for Ukrainians who had already been turned down. But, he failed to register as an agent for Burisma or Ukraine.

That is a violation of the law under FARA. But, Hunter could not register as a foreign agent as his father was vice president at the time and the optics would have been enormously bad. Therefore, he apparently decided to break the law knowingly in order to protect his influence-peddling scheme.

Recent revelations from Hunter‚Äôs laptop tell how he used his daddy‚Äôs name all over the world. The first email was revealed by Miranda DeVine and contained 22 talking points on Ukraine that Hunter sent to Devon Archer in order to aid Burisma 2 weeks before Joe was scheduled to arrive,

Here is a screenshot of Hunter Biden‚Äôs original 22-point Ukraine email cited in the column. Note the strategic detail. http://pic.twitter.com/kt6GNdQD85

‚Äî Miranda Devine (@mirandadevine) January 23, 2023

The second email showed that Hunter shared classified documents with Burisma for them to use to their advantage in dealing with the United States. He was also to help in getting visas for Burisma employees.

From The Gateway Pundit

In the email string below taken from the Hunter laptop, Sandweg emailed Eric Schwerin at Rosemont Seneca (Hunter Biden‚Äôs firm) on November 2, 2015. Sandveg relayed information on one of the individuals from Burisma for whom Hunter was trying to get a visa for was Mr. Zlochevskyi.

Sandweg in his email says that he obtained a search:

‚Ä¶from the Department of Homeland Security and Customs databases did not reveal any prohibitions on Mr. Zlochevskyi ability to enter the United States. Unfortunately, after receiving the initial report, I suspected that the individual I asked to run the search only queried DHS/Customs databases and not State Department databases. As such, I asked another individual to query both databases. This search revealed the cancellation of the visa and the legal basis for the cancellation.

Sandweg includes two attachments, one of which is labeled ‚ÄúZlochevski Visa Denial‚Äù.

Email number three:

On Monday TGP uncovered a third email showing more Biden family crimes related to classified information and espionage.

The email discovered on Hunter Biden‚Äôs laptop was sent from Blue Star Strategies, a firm that has reportedly been under investigation by the DOJ since 2021. The email that was sent in December 2015 had an attachment that included classified information from a White House conference call on Joe Biden‚Äôs upcoming trip to Ukraine. This email was also sent to Burisma and it implicates Joe Biden.

And number 4 related to Hunter not registering as a foreign agent.

From The Gateway Pundit

In 2017 General Michael Flynn was sentenced and along with it he was also forced to admit to ‚Äúmaking materially false statements in multiple documents filed pursuant to FARA.‚Äù The DOJ reportedly obtained Flynn‚Äôs guilty plea by threatening his son with the alleged crime of not filling out a FARA application.

In 2018, Paul Manafort ‚Äúpleaded guilty in the District of Columbia to two counts: (i) conspiracy to commit multiple offenses, including violating FARA by failing to register and by providing false statements in a document filed with FARA.‚Äù Manafort was sent to prison.

FARA violations were used against these two individuals who were close to President Trump.

In Hunter‚Äôs laptop were a number of emails that show that Hunter Biden acted as a foreign agent. Hunter‚Äôs actions in Ukraine with Burisma were one example.
